277
00:34:22,150 --> 00:34:23,380
I’m really sorry.

278
00:35:21,900 --> 00:35:24,620
Nop. Nop….it’s me.

279
00:35:25,100 --> 00:35:25,920
Aunty…

280
00:35:26,560 --> 00:35:28,440
Give him some water.

281
00:35:28,460 --> 00:35:33,870
Drink up, kiddo.

282
00:35:45,870 --> 00:35:50,250
