305
00:38:03,710 --> 00:38:07,500
Please let her go. I beg you. Please!!

306
00:38:08,100 --> 00:38:09,450
I beg you. Please!!

307
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:14,520
Get out of here! Now!

308
00:38:14,540 --> 00:38:15,140
Let’s go now

