342
00:45:07,450 --> 00:45:09,260
And you disappeared.

343
00:45:09,570 --> 00:45:12,080
You promised you’d stay to take care of me.

344
00:45:14,780 --> 00:45:19,230
Yeah right. Am I that worthless? Everyone’s leaving me

